result.name: Soup Plus

reviews.text: Just great dining in and food just fine.

nice selection of soup dishes. soup is definitely boiled with lots of ingredients. affordable and popular with students. accept cash only. always a crowd and queue during peak hours. be there early to avoid waiting. drinks selection is good too with my favourite red bean milk ice. good for sharing. place is small so not suitable  for a big group.
Food and service both are good.  I get what I paid for.
Decent prices, seafood is actually surprisingly good-especially the prawns, highly reconmend. Just a bit of an eyesore seating arrangement (same as all local restaurants)
Great food. Reasonable price.

result.adr_address: 香港石塘咀屈地街
result.name: 湯加

reviews.text: 冷氣坏了很久，很熱🥵🥵
叫了個鯇魚腩湯飯，魚肉不新鮮兼不熟，換了魚片，情況一樣……極難食，不會再光顧。
Just great dining in and food just fine.
食物味道是可以的。有味精。魚湯味道很咸。地方不太整潔，坐得不太自在。

今晚去 到 覺得比兩個女待應玩， 因為我 同同事4 人打完羽毛球去 食野。 4 個人，4 個餐，點知待應出單 係 5個餐，見到唔對路就 即時同 待應講返，其實我個餐重覆左。 之後待應打回一張 4 個餐既比我地。 之後其他3 個餐都 到左 , 之後過左 20分鐘左右，其他同事都食到 中段， 我再問 我 個餐有冇漏單， 佢 查完回覆我整緊。我再等，等到 同事都就食完，我再問其實係咪漏左單， 如果一直都冇整過我 就唔要了。 之後個待應去睇單，睇完，完全冇回覆是否漏左， 亦沒有道歉。 到 我 同事幫我問待應現在其實落左單未，待應才告訢我同事無。今時今日呢d 服務態度真係好有問題。

reviews.text: Really nice soup for 45 HK$ which you can mix with the ingredients you like. The people working there were also friendly, which is always a plus in this town
Oxtail soup is tender and flavorful. Good place to have a quick meal since the soups are premade and come out right away.
Average, soup is OK, potion is a bit small for guys.
Great place for fast dinner
